[0.013, "o", "../../engine/agent build life-engine\r\n"]
[25.284, "o", "Done. Files under `src/life-engine/`:\r\n\r\n- `engine.js` ‚Äî ES module, pure functions: `createGrid`, `get/set`, `neighbors` (toroidal), `step` (immutable), `stamp`, `PATTERNS` (glider, blinker), `randomSoup`. Works in node + browser, zero deps.\r\n- `selftest.mjs` ‚Äî asserts blinker period-2, glider translates (+1,+1)/4 steps, wrap survival at edge, soup density.\r\n- `check.sh` ‚Äî runs selftest, passes.\r\n"]
[0.009, "o", "bash src/life-engine/check.sh\r\n"]
[0.056, "o", "life-engine: all tests passed\r\n"]
[0.003, "o", "touch build/life-engine.done\r\n"]
[0.008, "o", "../../engine/agent build canvas-renderer\r\n"]
[47.150, "o", "Done. Files:\r\n\r\n- `src/canvas-renderer/renderer.js` ‚Äî age buffer (`createRenderState`/`updateAges`), smoothstep `alphaFor`, hue-shift `colorFor`, `draw` (dying/young cells shrink + fade), `startLoop` (rAF, fixed step interval, returns state for pause/toggle).\r\n- `src/canvas-renderer/selftest.mjs` ‚Äî asserts fade-in ramp, clamp at 1, fade-out trail, clamp at 0, alpha ease, blinker integration with life-engine (trail alpha between 0 and live alpha).\r\n- `src/canvas-renderer/check.sh` ‚Äî runs selftest, passes.\r\n\r\nponytail: no OffscreenCanvas/node-canvas dep ‚Äî draw path untested in node, math path fully tested. app-shell smoke test covers actual canvas.\r\n"]
[0.008, "o", "bash src/canvas-renderer/check.sh\r\n"]
[0.053, "o", "canvas-renderer selftest OK\r\n"]
[0.003, "o", "touch build/canvas-renderer.done\r\n"]
[0.005, "o", "../../engine/agent build app-shell\r\n"]
[45.888, "o", "Done. Files under `src/app-shell/`:\r\n\r\n- `index.html` ‚Äî canvas + Pause/Reset buttons + speed slider, loads `app.js` as module\r\n- `app.js` ‚Äî `initApp(doc)` wires random soup auto-start, play/pause toggle, speed slider (470‚Üí20ms), reset, click-to-toggle cells; imports siblings via relative paths\r\n- `selftest.mjs` ‚Äî headless smoke: stub DOM + rAF, init, tick 20 generations via fake clock, asserts evolution, pause, cell toggle, speed change\r\n- `check.sh` ‚Äî runs selftest, exits 0. No server needed (ponytail: pure DOM stubs instead of headless browser; upgrade path = playwright if real-browser check ever required).\r\n"]
[0.009, "o", "bash src/app-shell/check.sh\r\n"]
[0.071, "o", "app-shell selftest OK\r\n"]
[0.003, "o", "touch build/app-shell.done\r\n"]
